Class LynxSetSingleDIOOutputCommand

  • public class LynxSetSingleDIOOutputCommand
extends LynxDekaInterfaceCommand<LynxAck>
    Set the specified DIO pin to the given value. Setting the value of a DIO pin configured for input will result in a NACK. All DIO pins default to input until SetDIODirection is called to change them to output. There may be brief output glitches at startup.
